.demo-description
  %p
    The basic dialog window is an overlay positioned within the viewport and is protected from page content
    (like select elements) shining through with an iframe.  It has a title bar and a content area,
    and can be moved, resized and closed with the 'x' icon by default.
/ End demo-description
